headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 3X GTA$ and RP on Casino Story Missions and Casino Work
content: Help Agatha Baker and the Chengs fight off a hostile takeover at the hands of the Duggans in Casino Story Missions, or call Ms. Baker to request some Casino Work and assist with the maintenance of the house, so to speak. Both are paying out 3X GTA$ and RP this week.
